Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众生皆在我之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone is beneath me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众生皆在我之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone is beneath me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些小丑能不能安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you clowns be quiet?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要冥想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am trying to meditate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天啊  我们太吵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my stars, were we too loud?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考虑一下我们有多难堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagine our embarrassment
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.03,0:01:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这垃圾就得倒垃圾车  别倒我家草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The trash goes in the truck, not on my lawn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.99,0:01:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这垃圾你们该倒哪倒哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just put the garbage where it's supposed to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会该倒哪倒哪去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll put it exactly where it's supposed to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My roof
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,运气真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,臭了六个月之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,388)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡打包外带马上来  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's one Krabby Patty to go coming right up, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your order, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在想  等我醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking I'm gonna wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要面对午餐高峰期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back in the lunch rush
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经休息五分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been on my break for five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满脑子想的却只有下一单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all I can think about is getting my next order
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛躺在地上  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you on the floor, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在休息而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just taking a break
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since when did you start taking breaks?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我开始干我自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since I started doing both my job
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要兼顾章鱼哥的工作就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squidward's at the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥今天没出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward didn't show up today?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥已经六个月没来上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward hasn't come to work in six months
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我实在跟不上速度了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't keep up the pace, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去他家看看他有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go to his house to see if he's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身上可是担着两份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have two jobs to cover
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下班了才可以去看章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can go visit Squidward when you're off the clock
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定他在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure he's in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他的信箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at his mailbox
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有他家传出来的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that smell coming from his house
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unusual
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为是我的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们真的应该检查下他的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We really should check up on him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  反正我闲着没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, I got nothing better to do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you home?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥把这地方搞得乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's really let the place go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们令我想起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You remind me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位海绵宝宝和一位派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a SpongeBob and a Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在外面的世界认识了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew in the outer world
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候  潜入垃圾堆能找到收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you dumpster dive and find collectibles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他时候  下场都是迷失在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,other times you end up lost
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个无穷无尽的垃圾世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in an un-ending trash world
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.09,0:04:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有看到章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不认识什么章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know any Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你们可以问尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you could ask the Exalted One
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who now?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿我能用言语形容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only wish I had the words
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无足轻重  就是个零蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am nothing, a zero
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他完美无瑕  是垃圾之爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's perfection, the duke of debris
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知不知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he is or not?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往那边走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go that way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然这场旅途漫长又凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a long and treacherous journey
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们仍然继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we press on
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾的沼气四处弥漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Garbage gas is everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,似乎还会害人变笨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it seems to be making people silly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你旁白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your narrating
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得上个厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I gotta use the can
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能把那边那本杂志递给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could you hand me that magazine over there?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能得拉一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This might take a while
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太强了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Righteous, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个深不见底的裂谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bottomless chasm
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.05,0:06:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么跨过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we going to cross that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来章鱼哥只好失踪一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess Squidward's lost forever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆在打牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Urchins play cards?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不止是牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not just cards
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.12,0:06:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是桥牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想的跟我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tiny sandwiches
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有局纸牌友谊赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a friendly card game is right here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我好爱打桥牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, do I love to play bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有没有位置给给我们俩呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys got room for two mor--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有头翼龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pterodactyl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿到三明治了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the sandwiches
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿到牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got the cards
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,桥牌要怎么帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are bridge cards gonna help?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以建造一座悬置不信的大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By building a suspension of disbelief bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.96,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 悬置不信：欣赏作品时暂时不去质疑真实性 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没打中我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Missed me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尊者的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Exalted One's lair
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay out"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们虽然坚持到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made it this far
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.78,0:08:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还是必须通过前方的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you still must pass the booby traps up ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着像某种袜子管道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like some sort of tube of socks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是臭袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stinky socks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy does it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刮风了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breeze
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好臭的味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That smell
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这湖肯定是纯垃圾水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This lagoon must be pure garbage juice
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不要被它碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so don't let it touch--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥应该就在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think this is where Squidward is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说的可是尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You speak of the Exalted One
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾王公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the raja of rubbish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.22,0:08:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:08:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在可是超越了章鱼哥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is beyond Squidward now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.10,0:09:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是超越了消费与分解循环的伟人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is a great man who has risen above
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the cycle of consuming and discarding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.15,0:09:15.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一直在垃圾深处等候着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:15.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He has been waiting in the heart of garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enter
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里面的垃圾沼气也太难闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The garbage gas is really stinky in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害得我头晕目眩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's making me dizzy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.25,0:09:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没比平常晕多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more than usual
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人的价值是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the value of a man?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜的价格有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the price of a pickle?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就慢慢去琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you ponder that, man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吹点炫酷的曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to play something sick-el
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星快看  大家都很爱听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick, everyone is into it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沼气影响了他的心智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The gas has affected his mind
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来救你出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've come to get you out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是个打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but an errand boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  他是个做蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he's a patty laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty laddie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  是蟹堡王那个做蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a patty laddie from the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是同事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We worked there together
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开始想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to remember
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hated my job
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星还是你邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Patrick and I are your neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还恨我的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hated my neighbors too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家为什么全是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is my home filled with garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么臭味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what is that gassy smell?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家全废了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My place is ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用光照一下就能看清这片废墟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can see the ruin better in the light
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我带了这个点满蜡烛的烛台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I brought this fully lit candelabra
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.02,0:11:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别别别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  有沼气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, the gas
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少垃圾再也没在你家里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least the garbage isn't in your house anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史上最烂垃圾邪教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worst garbage cult ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My house
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天上班见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at work tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exalted One
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,508)}请勿打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.85,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}手办痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:52.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,418)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买特别款收藏品蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your collectible special edition Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1488,330)}特别款
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1402,274)}腌椰菜堡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with extra pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欲购从速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Act now
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数量有限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Supplies are limited
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要六个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want six
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都借过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outta my way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我呢  是个著名的胡子学家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am, uh, a prominent mustache-ologist
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.51,0:12:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要来个特别款的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I would like a special edition Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡子学家是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mustache-ologist, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了个真的胡子专家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real mustache expert
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有好多问题想请教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have so many questions
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比较喜欢润须蜡还是胡须护理油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer mustache wax or beard oil?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就有点难回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a tough one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡须护理油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beard oil?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡须护理油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beard oil?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都知道润须蜡才更好用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows mustache wax is superior
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你以为我这卷须是怎么长的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How else do you think I got these whiskery curls
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个所谓的专家完全就不懂胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This so-called expert
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doesn't know a thing about mustaches
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得会闻到有什么绿玩意臭臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I smelled something green and stinky
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假胡子不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice fake mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那胡子可是我花了六个月长出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent six months growing that mustache
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡永远也到不了手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它又不会就这么走出餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's gonna just walk out of the restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,端在银盘子上白白送我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a silver platter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.98,0:13:27.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的特别款蟹黄堡收藏又多了个精品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another excellent addition to my collection
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:27.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of special edition Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被打脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stand corrected
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷到蟹黄堡的机会终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my chance to finally get a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.33,0:13:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还没那个该死的老螃蟹碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without that blasted Krabs getting in my way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一天最多只能偷一次蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I have a one-caper-a-day maximum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回家整理自己的硬盘碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to defrag my hard drive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我只能自个搭车了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to hitch my own ride
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事就到地下室找我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the basement
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.86,0:14:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在我收藏家小金库一定会平平安安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be nice and safe in my secure collector's vault
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该把你放哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where should I put you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小小宝贝蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my precious little patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让它挨着我的爱聊堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll place it next to my Chatty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥肥堡和顽童堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fatty, and Bratty Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王  快上来帮我搓脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass, get up here and rub my tootsies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于能偷到一个蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally obtain a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多亏有那个白痴阿宅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks to that goofy geek
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让那个土肥圆发现我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't let that bulbous buffoon find me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我现身  可恶的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, foul intruder
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.60,0:15:24.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的特别款邪恶臭蛞蝓加超级黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:24.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My special edition Sinister Slug with super slime
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得重新把包装封好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to re-seal the package
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像全新未拆封的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like it was never opened
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再惹出麻烦来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now don't go causing any more trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  我的小可爱们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon, my lovelies
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的润足霜都快凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My foot butter is getting cold
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来取我的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to get my Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能碰上问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may have a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦肯定会发现我不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Karen will notice that I'm gone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后过来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and come find me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是比海霸糊好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it still tastes better than chum
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几周后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,740)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,硬盘碎片彻底整理干净最爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a thorough defragging
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eh, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好检查下他平常会去的老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better check the usual spots
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来这里偷秘方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here to steal the secret formula again?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  我下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm off the clock
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我只是在找痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just looking for Plankton actually
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有看到他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Golly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好几周都没看到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him in weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是先检查下抓痞老板的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's check all the Plankton traps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just in case
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Empty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not here either
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会躲在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where could he be hiding?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会帮你追踪到痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help you track Plankton down
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,追踪他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Track him?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给痞老板安装了个追踪芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I installed a tracking chip on Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以防他被冲进下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in case he got washed down the drain
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经不止一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板的信号是从那里传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's signal is coming from that way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一点黏液也吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the last of the goo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能吃自己的四肢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll move on to my limbs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.38,0:17:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  可以用这东西烧出一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I can use this to burn a hole
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大到可以让我逃出这个古怪玩具监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,big enough to get out of this kooky toy prison
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的邪恶臭蛞蝓玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Sinister Slug toy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你是怎么跑到这下面来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how did you get down here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈一定又在做有氧运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother must have been practicing her aerobics again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是我的官方正版
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe my official
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩祛痘霜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacle Boy acne cream has arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是你们俩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you two
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How disappointing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is Plankton here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绿色矮个  有股海霸糊味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Short, green, smells like chum
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.76,0:18:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不跟这种肮脏的家伙一起混
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not associate with such sordid individuals
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是你的追踪装置坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe your tracker's on the blink
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在里面没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们晚点再来侦察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's come back later for a little reconnaissance
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我反锁起来是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lock me away, will ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我给这些塑料玩意重新接线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once I rewire these plastic doodads
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改装成万能遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a universal remote
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能控制这些玩具  击倒那个宅男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take over these toys, knock that nerd out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grab the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and escape
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.09,0:19:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,当晚的晚些时候
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  计划如下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the plan:
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你关掉监控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you disable the surveillance cameras
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我逆向破解进门的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll reverse engineer the access codes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我的磁谐振器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and use my magnetic resonator
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,解锁安全系数极高的插销锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to unlock the high security deadbolt locks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这扇窗户没锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This window's unlocked
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬窗户也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or we could use the window
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一定就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He must be in there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.88,0:19:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定是某种脸部识别扫描器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be some kind of facial recognition scanner
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意应该不是刷脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think those are the right kind of cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这扫描器是刷屁股的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a booty-metric scanner
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得找海霸王才打得开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll need Bubble Bass to open it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事就到地下室找我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the basement
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要整理我的美人鱼战士收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,organizing my Mermaid Man memorabilia
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你咋不去整理简历
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you organize your resume
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找个班上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get a job?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to hide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能等他睡着了再行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to wait until he falls asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该可以稍微加速一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I can speed things up a little
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三重色氨酸火鸡蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A triple tryptophan turkey Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感恩节限定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Thanksgiving exclusive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈教过我不要对礼物吹毛求疵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother told me never look a gift patty in the buns
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃完火鸡堡就没有一个不晕过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one is immune to the ol' post-turkey patty food coma
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受死吧  你这臭白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to meet your doom, you smelly simpleton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.88,0:21:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿痞老板  马上给我从那里下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon J. Plankton, you come down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from there this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉刚刚朝你发射导弹  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the missiles, sweetie pie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在吵什么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is all that racket?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩具贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toy thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.73,0:21:42.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动终极封锁程序
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:42.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Activate ultimate lockdown protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1478,322)}恐慌
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.11,0:21:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些泡沫塑料能让我地下室所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These packing peanuts will preserve
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everything in my basement
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持九九新的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in mint condition
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's dinner time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上楼做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So get up here and start cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在又在乱搞什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What nonsense is he up to now?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又在里面玩玩具了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you playing with your toys in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.73,0:22:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用这个让你跟你朋友长长记性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let this be a lesson to you and your little friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准在家里面鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not to horse around in the house
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
